{"tid":546554,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"著左引擎燈，重接電池就熄番，係咩問題?","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T19:03:11.000Z","uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"90144cbfa89774ef6a01e3c51e281fce7e5a875f","tid":546554,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"呢排已經出現過幾次<br />\n著車行一陣，得C燈著，個&quot;C&quot;燈一熄，引擎燈就著<br />\n<br />\n唔記得google到邊度，話試下重接電池，即係拔左負極一陣再接番<br />\n又真係熄番引擎燈<br />\n<br />\n唔覺有怪聲，行車都暢順<br />\n電池只換左3個月，亦有電<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟係乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最搞笑係我上星期先政府驗車黎，又無問題bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9a897e85fb19a7b1b12b9d256ae7aa2abf6e5e","tid":546554,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef5d9bc3037ff6918a5fbf2c3b7f3325bc384e4","tid":546554,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93d99d0235311da89d40a108a6036ae6d73c674a","tid":546554,"uid":42407,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:02:52.000Z","msg":"寶麣鬱灤𧖣"},{"pid":"ee50422910ad5c8d517a76a64589e1ed32a4396c","tid":546554,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11d67b91137714c76448b4af080f648b15a6df26","tid":546554,"uid":38858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"重接電池= reset電腦錯誤碼<br />\n行多排又會著反"},{"pid":"d610c1d91bcc63ed5517a7dbc0b9df0f195356e2","tid":546554,"u